BILL PAYMENT
There are several convenient options available for you to pay your LEXserv bill promptly.
· Enroll in LEXserv AutoPay to have your LEXserv bill payment automatically deducted from your bank account on the day that it is due.
Visit www.LexingtonKY.gov/LEXserv at any time to enroll.
· Fill in the Amount Paid on the Remittance Form on the front of this bill. Detach and mail in return envelope with your check for the amount
due made payable to: Lexington-Fayette Urban County Government. Please include your account number on your check.
· Pay your LEXserv bill In person at the Revenue Office located at the Switow Building, 218 E. Main Street, Lexington, KY.
There is a small service fee for the following payment options. Fees vary depending upon payment option selected:
· Call LEXserv Customer Service at 1-888-987-8111 and select the option to pay your bill over the phone. You may pay by credit card or by debit
card.
· LEXserv WebConnect is available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week without registering or logging on. Make single payments using a credit or debit
card by visiting our QuickPay secure site.
Please pay your LEXserv City Services bill promptly for receipt by the due date.
Delinquent bills will incur a 10% penalty on the outstanding balance plus additional interest charges.
Failure to pay your LEXserv bill may result in shut-off of your water service.
If your LEXserv account is in immediate jeopardy of disconnection or if your water has been turned off as a result of a delinquent
LEXserv account, you must pay in person by cash, money order or credit card at 218 East Main Street in Lexington.
EMERGENCIES
For the following situations, please call LexCall at 311 (or 859-425-2255) during the hours of 8:00 am - 6:00 pm, Monday - Friday. Outside of normal
business hours, please call 859-335-2716 and press 0. LexCall creates a record of your call and helps us respond in the quickest, most efficient way.
· To report a sanitary sewer emergency
· To report an odor issue or any other sanitary sewer concern
If you have an emergency with your water service, please call Kentucky American Water at 1-800-678-6301.
CUSTOMER SERVICE
To make changes to your LEXserv City Services account, or for answers to questions about your bill, please call a LEXserv Customer Service
Representative at 1-888-987-8111.
